<%- include('../partials/mainHeader', { title: 'Support — Resurge: Interview Analytics', activePage: 'support' }) %>

    <main class="snap-container" id="snap-main" style="padding-top:62px;">

        <section class="snap-section" style="justify-content:center;">
            <div class="support-hero-grid">
                <div class="support-visual-wrap reveal-left">
                    <div class="hero-orb hero-orb-s1"><i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i></div>
                    <div class="hero-orb hero-orb-s2"><i class="fa-regular fa-comments"></i></div>
                    <div class="hero-orb hero-orb-s3"><i class="fa-solid fa-life-ring"></i></div>
                    <div class="hero-orb hero-orb-s4"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i></div>
                    <div class="support-stats">
                        <div class="support-status-header">
                            <div class="support-status-title">SUPPORT STATUS</div>
                            <div class="support-status-line"><span class="support-status-dot"></span>All systems operational</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="support-stat-row"><div class="support-stat-icon"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i></div><div><div class="support-stat-label">Response Time</div><div class="support-stat-value">&lt; 24h</div></div><div class="support-stat-badge support-badge-green">FAST</div></div>
                        <div class="support-stat-row"><div class="support-stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></div><div><div class="support-stat-label">Resolution Rate</div><div class="support-stat-value">97.4%</div></div><div class="support-stat-badge support-badge-blue">HIGH</div></div>
                        <div class="support-stat-row"><div class="support-stat-icon"><i class="fa-regular fa-comments"></i></div><div><div class="support-stat-label">Tickets Resolved</div><div class="support-stat-value">3,200+</div></div><div class="support-stat-badge support-badge-purple">ALL TIME</div></div>
                        <div class="support-stat-row"><div class="support-stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i></div><div><div class="support-stat-label">Satisfaction</div><div class="support-stat-value">4.9 / 5.0</div></div><div class="support-stat-badge support-badge-orange">RATED</div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal-right delay-100">
                    <div class="rsg-tag support-tag"><span class="accent-dot"></span> Help Center</div>
                    <h1 class="support-hero-heading">SUPPORT.</h1>
                    <p class="support-hero-body">Have questions or facing issues? Our team and comprehensive FAQ are here to help you get back on track with your interview analytics.</p>
                    <div class="support-cta-row"><a href="#faq" class="rsg-btn">Browse FAQs <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down"></i></a></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="snap-section support-section-bg">
            <div class="about-container reveal-up">
                <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
                <h2 class="about-heading">ABOUT RESURGE.</h2>
                <div class="about-grid">
                    <p class="about-para">Resurge is a comprehensive interview analytics platform dedicated to bridging the gap between candidate performance and professional success. By leveraging data-driven insights, the platform empowers job seekers to perform deep-dive analyses of their resumes and past interview experiences.</p>
                    <p class="about-para">Beyond its analytical tools, Resurge fosters a high-impact ecosystem through its active professional community — a collaborative space for candidates to exchange real-time interview experiences, discuss industry trends, and receive peer-to-peer mentorship.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="snap-section" id="faq">
            <div class="faq-container reveal-up">
                <span class="section-label">Got Questions?</span>
                <h2 class="faq-heading">FAQ.</h2>
                <div class="faq-list">
                    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-button"><span>What is Resurge and how can it help my career?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down faq-icon"></i></button><div class="faq-content"><div class="faq-content-inner">Resurge is an interview analytics and resume optimization platform designed to turn "near-misses" into job offers. We provide data-driven insights into why interviews may have stalled and offer actionable steps to improve your technical and behavioral presentation.</div></div></div>
                    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-button"><span>How does the resume analysis feature work?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down faq-icon"></i></button><div class="faq-content"><div class="faq-content-inner">Our system evaluates your resume against industry-standard benchmarks and specific job descriptions. It identifies gaps in your skill set, formatting issues, and keyword optimization to ensure your profile passes both automated tracking systems (ATS) and human recruiter reviews.</div></div></div>
                    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-button"><span>What kind of "failure analysis" does the platform provide?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down faq-icon"></i></button><div class="faq-content"><div class="faq-content-inner">After an interview, you can log your experience — including questions asked and your perceived performance. Resurge analyzes these inputs to identify patterns, such as struggle points in specific technical domains or recurring hurdles in cultural-fit rounds.</div></div></div>
                    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-button"><span>Is my interview data kept private?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down faq-icon"></i></button><div class="faq-content"><div class="faq-content-inner">Absolutely. Your personal interview logs and resume data are private to your account. You choose what information, if any, you wish to share with the community for feedback or discussion.</div></div></div>
                    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-button"><span>How can I interact with the Resurge community?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down faq-icon"></i></button><div class="faq-content"><div class="faq-content-inner">Resurge features dedicated forums and discussion hubs where users share real-time interview experiences, salary trends, and company-specific hiring processes. It is a space for peer-to-peer mentorship and collective growth.</div></div></div>
                    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-button"><span>Is Resurge suitable for entry-level candidates?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down faq-icon"></i></button><div class="faq-content"><div class="faq-content-inner">Yes. Whether you are a student preparing for your first placement or a seasoned professional looking to pivot, our analytics are scalable to various career stages and industries.</div></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="snap-section support-section-bg">
            <div class="contact-container reveal-up">
                <span class="section-label">Get in Touch</span>
                <h2 class="contact-heading">CONTACT.</h2>
                <p class="contact-body">Fill out the form below and our team will get back to you within 24 hours.</p>
                <form id="contact-form" class="contact-form" novalidate>
                    <div>
                        <label class="rsg-label" for="email">Email Address</label>
                        <input class="contact-input" type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="you@example.com" value="<%= locals.user ? locals.user.email : '' %>">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="rsg-label" for="subject">Subject</label>
                        <input class="contact-input" type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required placeholder="How can we help you?">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="rsg-label" for="content">Message</label>
                        <textarea class="contact-input" id="content" name="content" required placeholder="Provide as much detail as possible..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <button type="submit" id="contact-submit-btn" class="rsg-btn contact-send-btn">
                            Send Message &nbsp;<i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane" id="contact-btn-icon"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div id="contact-feedback" class="contact-feedback" style="display:none;"></div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="snap-section rsg-footer rsg-footer-wrap">
            <video autoplay muted loop playsinline class="footer-video" src="/assets/footer_animation.mp4"></video>
            <div class="footer-content-wrap">
                <div class="footer-grid">
                    <div><span class="footer-brand">RESURGE</span><p class="footer-tagline">Stop guessing. Start analyzing and visualizing your career path.</p><a href="/signUp" class="rsg-btn rsg-btn-footer">Join Now →</a></div>
                    <div><div class="footer-col-label">Platform</div><div class="footer-col-list"><a href="/resumeScore" class="footer-col-link">Resume Score</a><a href="/interviewLog" class="footer-col-link">Interview Log</a><a href="/dashboard" class="footer-col-link">Insights Dashboard</a></div></div>
                    <div><div class="footer-col-label">Legal</div><div class="footer-col-list"><a href="/404" class="footer-col-link">Privacy Policy</a><a href="/404" class="footer-col-link">Terms Of Use</a><a href="/404" class="footer-col-link">Cookie Settings</a></div></div>
                    <div><div class="footer-col-label">Connect</div><div class="footer-col-list"><a href="/404" class="footer-col-link"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i> &nbsp;GitHub</a><a href="/404" class="footer-col-link"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i> &nbsp;LinkedIn</a><a href="/404" class="footer-col-link"><i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter"></i> &nbsp;Twitter</a></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-marquee-strip"><div class="footer-marquee-track"><span class="footer-marquee-word">ANALYZE</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">VISUALIZE</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">RESURGE</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">IMPROVE</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">TRACK</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">GROW</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">ANALYZE</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">VISUALIZE</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">RESURGE</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">IMPROVE</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">TRACK</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span><span class="footer-marquee-word">GROW</span><span class="footer-marquee-dot"></span></div></div>
                <div class="footer-bottom-bar"><span class="footer-copy">Resurge Analytics &copy; 2026</span><span class="footer-copy-right">Built for Career Growth</span></div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </main>

    <script src="/js/faq.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/contact.js"></script>
<%- include('../partials/mainFooter') %>
